Package: MomX
Title: Easily Install and Load the MomX Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Vincent", "Bonhomme", 
           email = "your.email@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The MomX ecosystem is a collection of R packages for morphometrics
    that work together naturally. This package is designed to make it easy to 
    install and load core MomX packages in a single step. Learn more about MomX 
    at <https://momx.github.io/MomX/>.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://momx.github.io/MomX/, https://github.com/MomX/MomX
